reviewText: Bought this for my daughter and son-in-law so they could practice lamaze breathing. I watched it before giving it to them and I thought it was informative and helpful, but I was a little disappointed they didn't show more of the breathing practice exercises. Other than that, I think this is a great dvd for expectant parents who want to deliver naturally.  Daughter and son-in-law found it helpful, and delivered naturally and drug free 9 pound 1 ounce beautiful baby girl!!
